# Spotify Web Playback SDK Configuration
# Get your Client ID from: https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard/applications
#
# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Create a Spotify Developer account at https://developer.spotify.com
# 2. Create a new application to get your Client ID
# 3. Add this redirect URI to your app settings: http://localhost:5173/
# 4. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your Client ID
#
VITE_SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here
